Description: Fetches data from three disparate data sources and allows user to perform analyses on them. It offers two core components: 1. A robust data retrieval and preparation infrastructure for wildfire, climate, and air quality index data and 2. A simple, informative, and interactive visualizations of the aforementioned datasets for California counties from 2011 through 2015.
URL: https://github.com/bradraff/wildviz
